name: "Tanara" The Arc Sword Holder
description: In the cyber verse, everyone wants to be the holder of "Arc Sword" the one sword with the power to destroy anything it touches. It is originally owned by " Trevan" the PeaceKeeper. Trevan was killed by the rebels. But he managed to keep the sword away from the rebels by hiding it inside his vault that can only be reached and opened by his daughter Tanara, who is Highly skilled Cyber worrier who now holding the arc sword to maintain peace in the cyber world like her father once did.
